To compile, type ... 

g++ DrEvol_Br.cpp -O3 -o DrEvol_Br

# in orochi
g++ DrEvol_Br.cpp -Wall -W -O3 -ffast-math -funroll-loops -fomit-frame-pointer -march=nocona -o DrEvol_Br 

# in mosix
-Wall -O3 -ffast-math -funroll-loops -fomit-frame-pointer -march=pentium4 

# in poole
-O3 -ffast-math -funroll-loops -fomit-frame-pointer -mpowerpc 

# in hpc
-Wall -O3 -ffast-math -funroll-loops -fomit-frame-pointer -march=pentium4 

# in bigdog
-Wall -O3 -ffast-math -funroll-loops -fomit-frame-pointer -march=pentium4 

(before compiling, you will probably want to change the name of some 
output files specified 
in DrEvolMultiX4.cpp) 

To run, type 

  ( time nohup DrEvol_Br infile=LargeTest.seq  inseed=inseed06.dat ) 
> & oLargeTest 
